snippet.textDisplay:
My grandparents were from Larkana. Due to partition, they moved to India. Growing up heard so many stories from them . I always loved Coke Studio music and very happy to see Coke Studio Pakistan feature a Sindhi song. I can't get enough of this
"Penje je sikke te tu Larkano ghumande !!" budhi kare dadho khush thi vyus !! 
Thank you for bringing this to the world !!
snippet.textOriginal:
My grandparents were from Larkana. Due to partition, they moved to India. Growing up heard so many stories from them . I always loved Coke Studio music and very happy to see Coke Studio Pakistan feature a Sindhi song. I can't get enough of this
"Penje je sikke te tu Larkano ghumande !!" budhi kare dadho khush thi vyus !! 
Thank you for bringing this to the world !!
